<p>Metroid Prime 4: Beyond has had a few tidbits of info spill out this year, with <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/metroid-prime-4-beyond-finally-gets-release-date-plus-samus-on-a-motorbike">the release date was finally revealed back in September</a>. There's also been <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/voila-nintendo-quietly-shares-new-details-on-samuss-motorbike-in-metroid-prime-4">some information released about the motorbike too</a>, which may be worth reading for those interested in seeing what's new in Prime 4.</p>
<p>Metroid Prime 4: Beyond is set to release on the 4th December, on the Nintendo Switch and the Nintendo Switch 2.</p>

